  "title": "Sermon on the Mount §som_19_true_and_false_disciples: Not everyone who says to me, 'Lord, Lord,' will enter into the Kingdom of Hea...",
  "body": "Not everyone who says to me, 'Lord, Lord,' will enter into the Kingdom of Heaven; but he who does the will of my Father who is in heaven. Many will tell me in that day, 'Lord, Lord, didn't we prophesy in your name, in your name cast out demons, and in your name do many mighty works?' Then I will tell them, 'I never knew you. Depart from me, you who work iniquity.'",
